{"tid":1242563,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［定向討論集中地］21/6嘅去向太多講法，混亂嘅你入一入黎","createTime":"2019-06-19T05:54:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T11:19:20.000Z","uid":206352,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"34e8e85ab0f58d250b0a8dfd0ddaf72ecbd22431","tid":1242563,"uid":206352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:54:12.000Z","msg":"我地係之前嘅日子，69，612，616 都用有唔同嘅方式去為我地嘅家，香港，去抗爭。但結果係只行前咗一小步，而我地都付出咗好大嘅代價。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地嘅抗爭係未完㗎</span><br />\n<br />\n而對於進一步21/6嘅行動指我地依然混亂，所以希望大家係呢個post 集中討論，因為<span style=\"font-size: large;\">團結</span>將會係我地最大嘅籌碼。<br />\n<br />\n討論項目<br />\n1.行動目的+預計結果<br />\n2.地點<br />\n3.所採取的行動<br />\n4.派別的行動<br />\n<br />\n大家知道我地有5項目標，但必須要團結<br />\n例如我地係想警_為佢地嘅𣎴當付出代價嘅，會唔會係警總行動呢？<br />\n<br />\n最後,呢個post 係假設21/6的行動策劃，所以不支持21/6有所行動的請不要係到表態<br />\n<br />\n想出但唔知點做嘅都幫手推一推<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地需要嘅係策略同團結</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人，我地，仲可以繼續努力</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gi4FkF1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGi4FkF1.png&h=610b397f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f6ded3f61160904933e5cc6214e71b192dfa8fc","tid":1242563,"uid":206352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:56:18.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bcd5b4861ca96f0f89aef898f881a9417391134","tid":1242563,"uid":206352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:56:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c86b6fd4db2971ba5e74b7242467265a53035074","tid":1242563,"uid":49781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:58:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"44721569cbff325971154076574a0eaaef33eac7","tid":1242563,"uid":206352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:59:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"47d5542b4d09b6e8051cf4252a95cf2558b1d