":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T06:03:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">阻一阻你個post, 有d提議，認同請幫手推post：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n追究 警察濫權濫用武力 先係我地依家既王牌！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1242366\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1242366</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除左要傾行動細節<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">我覺得星期五 既 主題 應該要集中加強 於</span> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">追究警察濫權濫用武力 ！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">先講建議：</span><br />\n1. 將依項命題提高到 同反送中 一樣高度/重要性！<br />\n2. 老土d, 黎緊日子整多d 中英示威大Banner關於警察濫權、濫用暴力、同醫館局私通 既問題，追究責任！<br />\n3. 議員都應該要有共識去追究依個問題<br />\n4. 加強各種文宣。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">原因：</span><br />\n<br />\n關於行動主題，我地要識得運用火種<br />\n將香港人團怒火keep住燒：<br />\n<br />\n無錯，撤回係未達成，但人人都知個問題，團火已經係白熱化，所以口號照叫，但唔好只集中於依個命題；<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無錯，明日大嶼/雙普選/國歌法都係係大問題，但現實就係依幾個議題好難吸引到大多數市民，太新、太遠，我地可以將佢地加插入我地既討論，但好難成為民意大爆發既火種，只可以乘住其他議題去帶出。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反地，警察醫館局資料互通、差佬亂打青年人,和平示威者,女示威者、監警會無呀老虎，依d都係實實在在最令市民嬲既議題，亦都係國際社會既人權關注重點，我地一定要將依個命題加強到同反送中一樣高度！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68cb778944a39c90f677b1b2df9bf25ef8cfab0d","tid":1242563,"uid":258927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T06:03:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3878a92659918a2111c35a797b65113ec92239ae","tid":1242563,"uid":258927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T06:03:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40a21a7e4d307f9aff01812350d1bb1a718c7108","tid":1242563,"uid":258927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T06:03:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffc61fa258ce3e23822dde050ac939eeb8aff615","tid":1242563,"uid":66054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T06:03:40.000Z","msg":"6.21 發夢會衝既人請注意，切記得要冷靜，同埋避免先出手，唔好俾位人入，有藉口俾人話係暴徒。唔係既話民意會完全反cap，成個運動就會白廢。"},{"pid":"b2e20fe82de8726702afb3f6eb9d6a9c61fc2638","tid":1242563,"uid":258927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T06:03:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1fb54296500c6b1035e41514f2d77e895b360ae","tid":1242563,"uid":258927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T06:04:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/a